Interface CausalLink

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Ordering, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    POPCausalLink

    public interface CausalLink
extends Ordering
    Common interface for causal links (a causal link represents a step supporting a precondition of another step).
    Since:
    1.0
